rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units of absorbed dose rate, the standardized means of measuring the rate of absorbed dose, which is the mean energy imparted to matter per unit mass by ionizing radiation.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit of Absorbed Dose Rate

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.absorbed_dose_rate_unit to the mso:measurement_unit.measurement_system using this unit.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Measurement System

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit to the same amount as measured in one unit of grays per second.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Rate in Grays per Second

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units used to measure absorbed dose, which is a fundamental dose quantity representing the mean energy imparted to matter per unit mass by ionizing radiation.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit of Absorbed Dose

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.absorbed_dose_unit to its quantity when measured in grays.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Dose in Grays

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.absorbed_dose_unit to the mso:measurement_unit.measurement_system using this unit.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Measurement System

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all acceleration units, the units of measurement used to measure acceleration, the rate of change of velocity of an object.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit of Acceleration

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.acceleration_unit to its measurement of the same quantity in meters per second square.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Acceleration in Meters per Second Squared

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.acceleration_unit to the mso:measurement_unit.measurement_system using the unit.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Measurement System

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Value type collecting data on an adjusted monetary amount. Monetary amounts are adjusted by taking an original moneary value and adding or substracting certain amounts. For example, in the real GDP measurement, the nominal GDP amount is adjusted for price changes. In income tax terms in the United States, adjusted gross income is the total gross income minus specific reductions. Properties included on this are the adjusted value, the currency, and the measurement and adjustment dates.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Adjusted Money Value

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.adjusted_money_value to the value of the amount after adjustment.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Adjusted Amount

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.adjusted_money_value to the date to which the original measured value has been adjusted.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Adjusted Date

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.adjusted_money_value to the currency of the amount adjusted.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Currency

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.adjusted_money_value to the date the measurement was taken.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Measurement Date

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units of amount concentration.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit of Amount Concentration

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.amount_concentration_unit to its equivalent amount in moles per cubic meter.
Primary entity representing the units of measurement for angles.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit of Angle

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.angle_unit to the equivalent amount in radians.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Angle in Radians

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units of angular acceleration, the rate of change of angular velocity
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit of Angular Acceleration

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.angular_acceleration_unit to the equivalent amount in radians per second squared.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Acceleration in Radians per Second Squared

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units of angular velocity, which is the rate of change of angular displacement.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit of Angular Frequency

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.angular_velocity_unit to the equivalent amount in radians per second.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Frequency in Radians per Second

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units of area. These are the units that measure the extent of a two-dimensional figure or shape.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit Of Area

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.area_unit to the equivalent amount in square meters.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Area In Square Meters

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units of capacitance, which is the ability of a body to store an electrical charge.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit of Capacitance

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.capacitance_unit to the equivalent amount in farads.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Capacitance in Farads

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units of catalytic activity.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit of Catalytic Activity

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measure_unit.catalytic_activity_unit to the equivalent amount in katals.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Activity in Katals

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units of catalytic concentration.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit of Catalytic Concentration

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.catalytic_concentration_unit to the equivalent amount in katals per cubic meter.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Concentration in Katals per Cubic Meter

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Value type collecting data on the amount of change for a value. It holds the amount of change and the time period of the change.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Changed Value

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.changed_value to the amount of change that occurred during the given time period.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Amount Changed

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.changed_value to the units of change measured. For example, the amount may be of a type of currency, an amount of mass or volume, and so forth. If the unit is a type of currency, please use mso:measurement_unit.changed_value_over_time.currency_change
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Amount Time Unit

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.changed_value_over_time to the mso:finance.currency in which the amount_changed was measured. Note this property is a temporary workaround until finance.currency can be a subset of type.unit.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Currency

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that specifies the end of the date/time range over which the value varies.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: End Date

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that specifies the beginning of the date/time range over which the value varies.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Start Date

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.changed_value to the amount of time the change occurred.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Time Period

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.changed_value to the unit used to measure the time duration. Time may be measured in days, weeks, and years.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Time Unit

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units of electrical charge, which is the physical property of matter that causes it to experience a force when placed in an electromagnetic field
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit of Charge

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.charge_unit to the equivalent amount in coulombs.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Charge in Coulombs

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all common dimensions.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Common Dimension

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units of electric conductance, the ease with which an electric current passes through a conductor.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit of Conductance

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.conductance_unit to the equivalent amount in siemens.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Conductance in Siemens

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units of conductivity.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit of Conductivity

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.conductivity to the equivalent amount in siemens per meter.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Conductivity in Siemens per Meter

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units of current density, which is the electric current per unit area of cross section.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit of Current Density

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.current_density_unit to the equivalent amount in Amperes per Square Meter.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Density in Amperes per Square Meter

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units of electric current, which is the flow of electric charge.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit of Electric Current

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.current_unit to the equivalent amount in amperes.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Current in Amperes

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units of data size.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit of Data Size

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.data_size_unit to the equivalent amount in bytes.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Size In Bytes

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Type collecting the data on a dated float, including the date and value of the float.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Dated Float

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.dated_integer to the organization.organization that published or is the source of the data.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Data Source

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.dated_float to its date.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Date

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.dated_float to the mso:measurement_unit.dated_percentage.date_specification entity containing the date data for the float.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Date

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that restricts the numeric information to a particular location, if this is necessary, e.g. in cases of statistical data by country.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Location

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.dated_float to its value.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Number

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating the data contained in mso:measurement_unit.dated_integer to any associated mso:statistics.statistics_technique used to derive the data.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Statistics Method

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Type collecting the data on a statistic with a date, integer value, and base date range. For example, if an index measures food production, the data are collected over a given set of years with a date range that specifies what counts as the base for the statistic. If the date range is one year, the same year may be placed in both the start and end values of the mso:measurement_unit.time_interval
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Dated Float with Base Range

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.dated_float_base_date to the time interval that is the base date for the data. If the interval is one year, the same year may be entered in both the start and end dates.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Base Date

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.dated_float_base_date to the date the value is valid for. This is the validity date for the data. This is not the date(s) that provide the basis for the measurement; please see mso:measurement_unit.dated_float_base_date.base_time_interval for this property.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Date

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.dated_float_base_date to its decimal value.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Value
Dated Integer
rdf:Description.mso:type.type.deprecation_info: Use mso:measurement_unit.dated_float instead, as this item will not be supported. DeprecatedBy:[REDMOND\ianiles] Successor:[mso:measurement_unit.dated_float]

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: number
rdf:Description.mso:type.property.deprecation_info: Use mso:measurement_unit.dated_float.number instead, as this item will not be supported. DeprecatedBy:[REDMOND\ianiles] Successor:[mso:measurement_unit.dated_float.number]

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: date
rdf:Description.mso:type.property.deprecation_info: Use mso:measurement_unit.dated_float.date instead, as this item will not be supported. DeprecatedBy:[REDMOND\ianiles] Successor:[mso:measurement_unit.dated_float.date]

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Type collecting the data on a dated money entity. Data include the date, currency, and value amount.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Dated Money Value

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.dated_money_value to the monetary amount of the entity.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Amount

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.dated_money_value to the currency of the monetary amount.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Currency

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that specifies a specific date on which the money value is valid. Note that, for a given instance of measurement_unit.dated_money_value, only one of the following two properties should be used: measurement_unit.dated_money_value.valid_date or measurement_unit.dated_money_value.valid time_interval.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Valid Date

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that specifies the time interval over which the money value is valid. Note that, for a given instance of measurement_unit.dated_money_value, only one of the following two properties should be used: measurement_unit.dated_money_value.valid_date or measurement_unit.dated_money_value.valid time_interval.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Valid Time Interval

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Type collecting the data for a dated percentage. Data collected include source, rate, and date.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Dated Percentage

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:dated_percentage to the organization.organization that published or is the source of the data.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Data Source

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.dated_percentage to the date at which this value was accurate or measured.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Date

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.dated_percentage to the mso:measurement_unit.datetime_specification entity containing the date data for the percentage.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Date

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.dated_percentage to the percentage rate number, for example, 8.5 to represent 8.5%.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Rate

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating the data contained in mso:dated_percentage to any associated mso:statistics.statistics_technique used to derive the data.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Statistics Method

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Value type collecting data for a dated ratio, both the date and the numerator and denominator of the ratio.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Dated Ratio Type

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.dated_ratio to the date for which the ratio is valid.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Date

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.dated_ratio to the denominator of the ratio.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Denominator

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.dated_ratio to the numerator of the ratio.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Numerator

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A general type that collects information about dated numeric values.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Dated Value

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property specifying the point of time or the time interval over which the given value is valid.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Datetime Specification

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that specifies the location with respect to which the dated value is true.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Location

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that specifies, as a percentage, the margin of error for a dated value that is relative to the overall data set.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Relative Standard Error

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A type allowing a time reference to be represented as a single point or as an interval. This allows a single type to encompass all time references, and it allows for a certain amount of imprecision in the data. For example, in the case of birth date data, the data may be a specific date, e.g. June 22, 1974, or it may be a range, e.g. between 1950 and 1951.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Datetime Specification

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A Boolean property that indicates that the time specification is approximate. This is useful for historical dates that are often uncertain and prefixed with "circa", e.g. the date of birth of a historical figure might be given as circa 300 BC.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Approximate

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that provides a specific date.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Date

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property specifying the end of a date range.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Date Range End

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property specifying the start of a date range.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Date Range Start

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A type that is used to specify a range of days of the week, e.g. Monday through Friday or Saturday and Sunday.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Day Range

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that specifies the day of the week when the range begins.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Begin Day

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that specifies the day of the week when the range ends.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: End Day

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all dimensions. These are the magnitudes of given things in a particular direction. Instances include time, length, torque.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Dimension

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Virtual property relating an mso:measurement_unit.dimension to the mso:measurement_unit.measuring_instrument that is used to measure the dimension.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: instruments

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Type collecting data on the dimensions of a given object. Data include length, height, and width.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Dimensions

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property specifying the object's depth in meters.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Depth

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property specifying the object's diameter in meters.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Diameter

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property specifying the object's height in meters.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Height

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property specifying the object's length in meters.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Length

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property that specifies the type of dimensions measured, e.g. inner or outer.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Type

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property specifying the object's volume in liters.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Volume Liters

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: A property specifying the object's width in meters.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Width

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units of length.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit Of Length

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.distance_unit to the equivalent amount in meters.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Distance In Meters

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units of dose equivalence. These are the units used to measure the stochastic health effects of low levels of ionizing radiation on the human body.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit of Dose Equivalence

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.dose_equivalence_unit to the equivalent amount in sieverts.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Equivalence in Sieverts

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units of electric charge density, which is a measure of electric charge per unit volume of space.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit of Electric Charge Density

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.electric_charge_density_unit to its equivalent amount in coulombs per cubic meter.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Density in Coulombs per Cubic Meter

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units of electric field strength.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit of Electric Field Strength

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.electric_field_strength_unit to the equivalent amount in volts per meter.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Strength in Volts per Meter

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units of electric flux density.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit of Electric Flux Density

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.electric_flux_density_unit to the equivalent amount in coulombs per square meter.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Density in Coulombs per Square Meter

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units used to measure energy density, which is the amount of energy stored in a given system or region of space per unit volume or mass
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit of Energy Density

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.energy_density_unit to the equivalent amount in joules per cubic meter.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Density in Joules per Cubic Meter

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units used to measure energy.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit Of Energy

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.energy_unit to the equivalent amount in joules.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Energy in Joules

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units of exposure.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit of Exposure

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.exposure_unit to its equivalent amount in coulombs per kilogram.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Exposure in Coulombs per Kilogram

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Type collecting the data on a range of floats.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Floating Point Range

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.floating_point_range to the higher of the two values.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: High Value

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.floating_point_range to the lower of the two values.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Low Value

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units of torque, which is the tendency of a force to rotate an object about an axis, fulcrum, or pivot.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit of Moment of Force

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.force_moment_unit to the equivalent amount in newton meters.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Moment in Newton Meters

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units of fuel economy.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit of Fuel Economy

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: If this unit measures distance per volume, this property gives its equivalence, and should be exclusive of Economy in litres per kilometre.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Economy in kilometres per litre

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: If this unit measures volume per distance, this property gives its equivalence, and should be exclusive of Economy in kilometres per litre.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Economy in litres per kilometre

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Primary entity representing the collection of all units of heat capacity. Heat capacity is the ratio of the heat added to (or subtracted from) an object to the resulting temperature change.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Unit of Heat Capacity

rdf:Description.mso:type.object.description: Property relating an mso:measurement_unit.heat_capacity_unit to its equivalent amount in joules per Kelvin.
rdf:Description.mso:type.object.name: Capacity in Joules per Kelvin
